**`src/rate_limiter.py`** — Sliding window rate limiter using:
- A `deque` of `(timestamp, cost)` per client for O(1) append/evict
- A separate cost counter per client to avoid summing the deque on every call
- A single `threading.Lock` protecting all state, ensuring atomic check-and-grant
- Entries at exactly the window boundary (`<=` cutoff) are treated as expired

